Unbelievable! We made history!

FGC Team China, we won consecutive titles: Winning Alliance 2023 & 2024. So proud to present our Feeding The Future Robot

63501727527414_.pic_hd1920×2560 505 KB

  • See our CAD file on the OnShape: 2024 Robot CAD
  • See our codes on the GitHub: 2024 Robot Codes
  • See our Engineering Book to figure out our iterations and game analysis before making our final robot: 2024 Engineering Book

Most importantly, subscribe our Instagram to get latest news about us!

Feel free to ask any questions about us (no matter it is technical or not). We are glad to be here to answer these questions!
